**Related Rules**:
- [prd-doc.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/prd-doc.mdc) - PRD document structure and workflow for tracking requirement changes
- [dev-doc.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/dev-doc.mdc) - Development documentation (HOW to build) that implements these feature requirements
- [changeset-doc.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/changeset-doc.mdc) - Technical changes documentation

**Related Commands**:
- `/plan-ft` - Creates feature or PRD document
- `/plan-ft-dev` - Creates changeset document from feature/PRD
- `/wrap-context-docs` - Applies PRDs to feature docs and archives them
- `/requirements-change` - Guides decision on PRD vs direct update

**Workflow Integration**:
```
Feature requirement change → PRD → Changeset → Implementation → Wrap → Updated docs
```

